Quick installation:

1) You may need to edit the Makefile.
2) Type "make".
3) Run "make install" as root.
4) Create a configuration file (example provided as mmsrc.EXAMPLE) in
   $HOME/.mjsrc.  Set the path to the player and a couple of various
   options. This is also where you configure window sizes, positions and
   colors.
5) enjoy!
